{
  "texts": [
    "These images are high-resolution JPEG files with dimensions exceeding 2000 × 2000 pixels.",
    "In Layer 2, raw data undergoes preprocessing per the requirements of the DL model.",
    "The images are resized to dimensions of 224 × 224 × 3 and converted into PNG format.",
    "In this context, '224 × 224' signifies length and width, and '3' denotes the number of channels.",
    "Following preprocessing, data is separated between training and testing, with 70% allocated for training and 30% for testing."
  ]
}